  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/010f37e84711e3734f480c65f54d05f9.avif?t=1637883230\" width=600 height=70 /></span><br>Maze Garden is a cute and relaxing game, but one that can get you tense sometimes, where your goal will be to find the kittens and your main challenge will be not to get lost in a variety of <strong>50 different mazes</strong>. And be careful not to fall into the water or get burned on the way, as you'll have to restart the level.<br>The mazes were designed one-by-one to provide progressive difficulty, but some are intended to be very difficult, are you up to the challenge?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/597aa577e695c5d12d5d584600d1ff0d.avif?t=1637883230\" width=600 height=70 /></span><br><br>More than one character available to choose from.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/865e1ef1e69a26282874532a04be1d71.poster.avif?t=1637883230\" width=600 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/865e1ef1e69a26282874532a04be1d71.webm?t=1637883230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/865e1ef1e69a26282874532a04be1d71.mp4?t=1637883230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect coins to unlock new abilities and skins<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/dd0b568bbfc4f5deace0e2c357fd7515.poster.avif?t=1637883230\" width=600 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/dd0b568bbfc4f5deace0e2c357fd7515.webm?t=1637883230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/dd0b568bbfc4f5deace0e2c357fd7515.mp4?t=1637883230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>50 hand-crafted levels with increasing complexity and 50 achievements to be collected;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/d6656655d99528561d73db903acbc336.poster.avif?t=1637883230\" width=600 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/d6656655d99528561d73db903acbc336.webm?t=1637883230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/d6656655d99528561d73db903acbc336.mp4?t=1637883230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>2 theme options, Normal and Halloween, which you can choose to play in all stages. With themed decor and soundtrack.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/7e0c617c50a054f1eaa1a3ebba2e0b6e.poster.avif?t=1637883230\" width=600 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/7e0c617c50a054f1eaa1a3ebba2e0b6e.webm?t=1637883230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/7e0c617c50a054f1eaa1a3ebba2e0b6e.mp4?t=1637883230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Beautiful backgrounds in a cartoonish and cute pixel art style;<br>Original soundtrack created exclusively for the game;",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/010f37e84711e3734f480c65f54d05f9.avif?t=1637883230\" width=600 height=70 /></span><br>Maze Garden is a cute and relaxing game, but one that can get you tense sometimes, where your goal will be to find the kittens and your main challenge will be not to get lost in a variety of <strong>50 different mazes</strong>. And be careful not to fall into the water or get burned on the way, as you'll have to restart the level.<br>The mazes were designed one-by-one to provide progressive difficulty, but some are intended to be very difficult, are you up to the challenge?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/597aa577e695c5d12d5d584600d1ff0d.avif?t=1637883230\" width=600 height=70 /></span><br><br>More than one character available to choose from.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/865e1ef1e69a26282874532a04be1d71.poster.avif?t=1637883230\" width=600 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/865e1ef1e69a26282874532a04be1d71.webm?t=1637883230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/865e1ef1e69a26282874532a04be1d71.mp4?t=1637883230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect coins to unlock new abilities and skins<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/dd0b568bbfc4f5deace0e2c357fd7515.poster.avif?t=1637883230\" width=600 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/dd0b568bbfc4f5deace0e2c357fd7515.webm?t=1637883230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/dd0b568bbfc4f5deace0e2c357fd7515.mp4?t=1637883230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>50 hand-crafted levels with increasing complexity and 50 achievements to be collected;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/d6656655d99528561d73db903acbc336.poster.avif?t=1637883230\" width=600 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/d6656655d99528561d73db903acbc336.webm?t=1637883230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/d6656655d99528561d73db903acbc336.mp4?t=1637883230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>2 theme options, Normal and Halloween, which you can choose to play in all stages. With themed decor and soundtrack.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/7e0c617c50a054f1eaa1a3ebba2e0b6e.poster.avif?t=1637883230\" width=600 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/7e0c617c50a054f1eaa1a3ebba2e0b6e.webm?t=1637883230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674880/extras/7e0c617c50a054f1eaa1a3ebba2e0b6e.mp4?t=1637883230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Beautiful backgrounds in a cartoonish and cute pixel art style;<br>Original soundtrack created exclusively for the game;",
